    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.toc_title": "维护保养",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.header_ref": "CH.08 — MAINTENANCE",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.title": "真空包装特性",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.toc_title": "真空包装特性",
    "content.chapter.09-vacuum-properties.header_ref": "CH.09 — VACUUM PROPERTIES",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.title": "品牌与保修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.toc_title": "品牌与保修信息",
    "content.chapter.10-warranty.header_ref": "CH.10 — WARRANTY",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.1": "本机仅供家庭使用，请勿用于其他非设计用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.2": "请勿让儿童玩耍本机或电源线。儿童、行动不便或认知受限人士应在成年人监督下使用。使用期间请留意儿童，避免意外发生。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.3": "小零件、真空袋可能造成窒息危险，请勿让儿童接触。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.4": "请勿在高湿高温等环境使用本机。严禁在有易燃易爆气体的环境中使用。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.5": "请确保电源电压与机器铭牌标示一致。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.6": "机器工作时请勿离开。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.7": "密封完成后，密封区域温度较高，请勿触摸，以免烫伤。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.8": "使用后请切断电源。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.9": "从电源插座上拔出插头时请手握插头拔出，请勿拉扯电源线。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.10": "请勿将主机或电源线浸入水中或其他液体中。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.11": "电源线需要直接插接符合安全规范的电源插座上。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.12": "如发现插头、电源线或主机损坏，请立即停止使用并联系制造商或授权维修点处理，请勿自行拆修。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.item.13": "电源线请勿悬挂于台面边缘，以免儿童拉扯或意外绊倒。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.1.title": "警告 WARNING",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "请妥善保管本手册。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "本机无需添加任何润滑剂，请勿使用有机溶剂清洁。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "长时间不使用时，请勿扣上锁扣，以免密封圈受压变形。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.item.4": "请勿将本产品与生活垃圾一同丢弃，请根据您所在地区关于电子废弃物的法规进行回收或处置。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.2.title": "注意 CAUTION",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.1": "本产品适用于家庭食品保鲜用途。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.2": "首次使用前，请完整阅读本说明书。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.item.3": "请保留购买凭证，以便享受保修服务。",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.block.3.title": "提示 NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.01-safety.page.page1.section_title": "安全须知",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.1": "本机只适用于带有空气通道纹路的真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.2": "对于带有尖点或棱角的物品，需用防刺穿片、纸巾等柔软包材包裹棱角，以防刺破真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.3": "真空袋可用于加热或微波炉加热，但必须先在袋角剪开一个小口透气。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.4": "用于储存的真空袋可重复使用，但用于加热或微波加热时仅可使用一次。储存过海鲜或油腻食品的真空袋不建议重复使用。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.5": "放置袋子时，袋口必须平整地跨过发热器。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.6": "装袋时，请务必在袋口和食物之间预留至少 2 inch（5 cm）的空间。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.7": "装入液体、酱汁或带液体的食物时，请避免将真空袋袋口弄湿。建议装入后将袋口擦干，以免影响密封效果。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.8": "如果需要质地柔软、含水分多的食物在包装后保持形状，可选择冷冻后进行真空封装。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.block.1.item.9": "勿在面盖上放置重物，有可能损坏机器。",
    "content.chapter.02-usage-tips.page.page1.section_title": "产品及真空袋使用提示",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.block.3.text": "工作结束后，发热器温度很高，请不要触摸，以免烫伤！",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.block.3.title": "提示",
    "content.chapter.03-structure.page.page1.section_title": "产品结构",
    "content.chapter.04-functions.page.page1.section_title": "产品功能",
    "content.chapter.05-specifications.page.page1.section_title": "技术参数",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.1.text": "6.1 如何使用切袋刀",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "打开面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "打开切袋刀架。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "从卷袋上拉扯出所需长度的袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "将切袋刀移至最左或最右边，再使刀架下压着袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "将切袋刀下压滑动划过袋子，以进行整齐的切割。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.3.text": "6.2 如何使用密封功能",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.text": "**从卷袋中制作袋子并密封：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step1.text": "按以上如何使用切袋刀制作出一个两端开口的袋子。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step2.text": "将袋子的一端开口平整放入真空腔内。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step3.text": "关闭面盖，并将把手向下压以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.step.step4.text": "点击 [btn:Seal] 按键，并等待机器完成工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.text": "**单独密封袋子：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step1.text": "将袋子放入需要封装的物品，并将袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step2.text": "关闭面盖，并将把手下压以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.7.body.1.step.step3.text": "点击 [btn:Seal] 按键，并等待机器完成工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.text": "6.3 如何延长密封时间",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.text": "若需延长密封时间，需在操作前点击 [btn:Extend Seal Time] 按键，使该按键指示灯点亮。延长时间设置将持续生效。若要恢复默认密封时间，请在下一次操作前再次点击该按键。当机器进入休眠或断电重新开机，密封时间将会恢复默认设置。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.text": "启用 Extend Seal Time 功能时，将暂时禁用智能密封调节功能，连续工作时每次工作间隔需大于 20s，并打开面盖以便机器散热。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.title": "注意",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.1.text": "6.4 如何使用真空密封功能",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.2.text": "**真空密封固体物品：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step1.text": "将袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step2.text": "关闭面盖，并下压把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step3.text": "点击 [btn:Vac Mode] 按键选择模式：**Normal** 或 **Gentle**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step4.text": "点击 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按键启动工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.3.step.step5.text": "若需终止工作，请点击 [btn:Stop] 按键。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.4.text": "在采用 Gentle 模式封装贵重物品前，建议先采用其它物品尝试真空后的压缩程度是否满足需求，以免压碎物品。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.5.text": "**真空密封液体：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step1.text": "保持袋子直立，确保液体液面始终低于发热器，液体与袋口之间建议留出 7 inch（18 cm）的空间。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step2.text": "将袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step3.text": "关闭面盖，并下压把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step4.text": "点击 [btn:Vac Mode] 按键选择 **Liquid** 模式。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.block.6.body.1.step.step5.text": "点击 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按键启动工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page3.section_title": "操作指引（续）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.1.text": "6.5 如何使用手动真空",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.2.text": "**方法一（在自动真空过程中切换至 Pulse Vac 模式）：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step1.text": "长按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按键进行真空抽气。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step2.text": "松开按键则暂停抽气。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.3.step.step3.text": "达到所需真空状态后，点击 [btn:Seal] 按键进行密封。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.4.text": "**方法二（直接使用 Pulse Vac 模式）：**",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step1.text": "将袋口放入真空腔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step2.text": "关闭面盖，并下压把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step3.text": "长按 [btn:Pulse Vac] 按键进行真空抽气。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step4.text": "松开按键则暂停抽气。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.5.step.step5.text": "达到所需真空状态后，点击 [btn:Seal] 按键进行密封。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.block.6.text": "在手动真空过程中，长按按键抽气，松开暂停，此时会处于保压的状态。若 10 秒内不进行再次操作，机器将自动释放压力，并退出手动抽气模式。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page4.section_title": "操作指引（续）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.1.text": "6.6 真空软管用法",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.1": "对梅森罐适配器和带阀门拉链袋抽真空时，圆形吸嘴采用方向1。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.2": "对真空罐和瓶塞抽真空时，根据抽气口大小选择方向1或2。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.2.body.1.item.3": "真空软管扁形吸嘴3用于连接机器面盖上的外抽气口3。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.3.text": "6.7 如何抽梅森罐",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step1.text": "闭合机器面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step2.text": "将罐盖放到梅森罐罐口，不需拧上螺纹盖（如有）。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step3.text": "将适配器安装到梅森罐上。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step4.text": "将真空软管扁形吸嘴插入机器面盖上的外抽气孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step5.text": "压下把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step6.text": "点击 [btn:Accessories] 按键，选择 **Mason Jar**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step7.text": "将真空软管圆形吸嘴覆盖适配器的抽气孔，并用手轻微按压住。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step8.text": "点击 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按键启动工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.block.4.body.1.step.step9.text": "工作结束，取下真空软管及适配器。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page5.section_title": "操作指引（附件使用）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.1.text": "6.8 如何抽真空罐",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "操作前，请确认真空罐与本机真空软管兼容。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "确认真空罐处于可抽真空（Vacuum）的状态。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "将真空软管扁形吸嘴插入机器面盖上的外抽气孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "压下把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "点击 [btn:Accessories] 按键，选择 **Canister**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step6.text": "将真空软管圆形吸嘴覆盖真空罐抽气阀的抽气孔，并用手轻微压住。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step7.text": "点击 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 按键启动工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.block.2.body.1.step.step8.text": "工作结束，取下真空软管。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page6.section_title": "操作指引（附件使用）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.1.text": "6.9 如何腌制",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step1.text": "将食物覆盖酱料，并放到真空罐中。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step2.text": "确认真空罐处于可以抽真空（Vacuum）的状态。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step3.text": "将真空软管扁形吸嘴插入机器面盖上的外抽气孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step4.text": "将真空软管圆形吸嘴插入抽气阀的抽气孔。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step5.text": "压下把手以锁紧面盖。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step6.text": "点击 [btn:Accessories] 按键，选择 **Canister**。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step7.text": "点击 [btn:Vac&Seal / Start] 启动工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.block.2.body.1.step.step8.text": "工作结束，取下真空软管。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page7.section_title": "操作指引（续）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.1.text": "6.10 卷袋仓操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.1": "本机器可以同时放置两卷卷袋（例如：两卷小于等于 20 feet/6m 长的卷袋）。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.2": "若放置单卷袋，则最长可放置 50 feet（15m）长。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.block.2.item.3": "卷袋仓可容纳 12 inch（300mm）以下宽度的卷袋。底部为宽度在 8 inch（200mm）以下的卷袋设计了专用放置槽。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page8.section_title": "操作指引（续）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.1": "故障现象",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.2": "可能原因",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.3": "解决方案",
