    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.3": "确保袋子的开口全部在下真空腔密封圈内。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.1": "使用了非纹路真空袋",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.2": "确保使用带有纹路的真空袋。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.1": "密封圈破损、翻起或安装不正确",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.2": "检查密封圈状态并正确安装。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.1": "袋子破损或有针孔",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.2": "更换新的真空袋。",
